msgstr "登出(_L)…"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:141
msgid "_Extensions"
msgstr "擴充套件(_E)"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:146
msgid "More Information"
msgstr "更多資訊"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:158
msgid ""
"Extensions can cause performance and stability issues. It is recommended to "
"disable all extensions if you experience problems with your system."
msgstr ""
"擴充套件可能導致效能與穩定性問題。若您的系統遭遇問題，則建議停用全部的擴充套"
"件。"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:185
msgid "User Extensions"
msgstr "使用者擴充套件"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:194
msgid "System Extensions"
msgstr "系統擴充套件"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:213
msgid "Search Results"
msgstr "搜尋結果"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:227
msgid "No Results Found"
msgstr "找不到結果"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:228
msgid "Try a different search"
msgstr "嘗試不同的搜尋內容"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:239
msgid "No Installed Extensions"
msgstr "沒有已安裝的擴充套件"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:240
msgid ""
"To find and add extensions, visit <a href=\"https://"
"extensions.gnome.org\">extensions.gnome.org</a>."
msgstr ""
"要尋找並加入擴充套件，可以造訪 <a href=\"https://"
"extensions.gnome.org\">extensions.gnome.org</a>。"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:250
msgid "Something’s gone wrong"
msgstr "有些地方出錯了"

#: data/ui/extensions-window.ui:251
msgid ""
"We’re very sorry, but it was not possible to get the list of installed "
"extensions. Make sure you are logged into GNOME and try again."
msgstr ""
"非常抱歉，我們無法取得已安裝的擴充套件列表。請確認您已登入 GNOME 之後並重試看"
"看。"

